          <tr><td>Simmer orifice cleaning (included with service)</td><td>Free</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Burner base realignment (included)</td><td>Free</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Gas regulator (LP or NG)</td><td>$145 – $215</td></tr>
