          <p>Professional 7/5 Series ranges (cooktop + oven integrated). Same spark module family, different service category from standalone cooktops.</p>
          <span class="cat-cta">View range repair →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/brands/viking-oven-repair/" class="cat-card">
          <h3>Viking Wall Oven Repair</h3>
          <p>VSOE/VDOE wall ovens. Commonly paired with VGSU cooktops in luxury kitchens across Southern California where owners specify separate cooktop + wall oven instead of integrated range.</p>
          <span class="cat-cta">View wall oven repair →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/brands/viking-refrigerator-repair/" class="cat-card">
